  "title": "A person observed the same big round red UFO for two weeks in Curitiba [1997]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/23/a-person-observed-the-same-big-round-red-ufo-for-two-weeks-in-curitiba-1997/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-C2",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MAY 5th, 1997</strong>. Time: 20h00. Duration: &#8220;many hours&#8221;. &#8220;For two weeks, around 8:00 pm, from his home window&#8221; at Jardim Ipê, in Curitiba, State of Paraná, a person observed an unidentified flying object with a round shape and red-orange color. According to the witness, from his perspective, the UFO appeared to be &#8220;bigger than the moon in the sky&#8221; and positioned itself to the Northeast. The sighting was done with the naked eye and in good conditions of visibility, with a cloudless sky.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.488. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado avistado na região de Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
